"title": "5840: eagerness",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5840",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A willingness, zeal or longing to accomplish a task or fulfil an ambition.</p>\n<h2>Eagerness to perform a task</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr12:8\">1CH 12:8</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:20\">NEH 3:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra5:8\">EZR 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:13\">PRO 31:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:16\">ACT 20:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:17\">1TH 2:17</a></p>\n<h2>Eagerness to fulfil personal ambitions</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:7\">ZEP 3:7</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:10\">1TI 6:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps56:6\">PSA 56:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:11-Prov1:12\">PRO 1:11–1:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:20\">PRO 28:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:25\">MRK 6:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:17-Gal4:18\">GAL 4:17–4:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:6\">PHP 3:6</a></p>\n<h2>Eagerness for personal godliness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr15:15\">2CH 15:15</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:10\">2PE 1:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:9\">1CH 28:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:4\">PSA 27:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:1-Ps42:2\">PSA 42:1–42:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps63:1\">PSA 63:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:17\">PRO 23:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:7\">ACT 26:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:1\">1CO 14:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:11\">2CO 7:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:11\">HEB 4:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:11\">HEB 6:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:2\">1PE 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:5\">2PE 1:5</a></p>\n<h2>Spiritual eagerness may be superficial and unreal</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:2\">ISA 58:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:34-Ps78:37\">PSA 78:34–78:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:1\">ISA 48:1</a></p>\n<h2>Believers should be eager to follow and serve their Lord</h2>\n<h3>Eager to do good works</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:14\">TIT 2:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:7\">2CO 8:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:22\">2CO 8:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:1\">TIT 3:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:8\">TIT 3:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:14\">TIT 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:13\">1PE 3:13</a></p>\n<h3>Eager to serve</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:11\">ROM 12:11</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:2\">1PE 5:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps110:3\">PSA 110:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:8\">ROM 12:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:12\">1CO 14:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:3\">EPH 4:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:8\">TIT 3:8</a></p>\n<h3>Eager to share the truth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:15\">ROM 1:15</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:15\">2PE 1:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:25\">ACT 18:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:13\">ACT 21:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:20\">ROM 15:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:20\">PHP 1:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:3\">JUD 1:3</a></p>\n<h3>Eager to receive or understand the truth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:37\">MRK 12:37</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:33\">ACT 10:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:17\">MRK 10:17</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:16\">MAT 19:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:18\">LUK 18:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:15\">LUK 2:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:38\">LUK 21:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:40\">JHN 4:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:42\">ACT 13:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:11\">ACT 17:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:15\">1TI 4:15</a></p>\n<h3>Eager to give</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:7\">2CO 8:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:21-Exod35:22\">EXO 35:21–35:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:9\">1CH 29:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:11\">2CO 8:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:19\">2CO 8:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:10\">GAL 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:18\">1TI 6:18</a></p>\n<h3>Eager to pray</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:2\">COL 4:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:30\">ROM 15:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:3-Phil1:4\">PHP 1:3–1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:12\">COL 4:12</a></p>\n<h3>Eager for God's honour</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num25:11\">NUM 25:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:14\">1KI 19:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs10:16\">2KI 10:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:17\">JHN 2:17</a></p>\n<h3>Eager to see Jesus Christ's return and the end of the world</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:7\">1CO 1:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:44\">MAT 24:44</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:40\">LUK 12:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:19\">ROM 8:19</a> <em>Creation shares the same eager expectation</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:23\">ROM 8:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:5\">GAL 5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:20\">PHP 3:20</a></p>",
